  "synopsis": "Su Moting is a young working woman burdened with the identity of a \"child of a god and a demon.\" After being kicked out of her home by her parents under the pretext of \"independence and self-reliance,\" she encounters two other fallen human beings: a goofy but handsome little god named Tianjixing and a mysterious, calm, and cool cat demon named Dikui. Under the guidance of the Earth God, the three form a savior team and begin their hilarious yet heart-wrenching daily lives.\n\n(Source: Bilibili, translated)",
